  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN THE COMMUNITY ON DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Operation Valor is a tactical top-down multiplayer shooter that provides large-scale combat through base building and teamwork. Players will fight across diverse battlefields with squad-based action in vehicles, or on foot. Prepare for an exciting battle utilizing strategy, logistics, and base building. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/777213f909e4b8e94e62f6c17a04513f.poster.avif?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/777213f909e4b8e94e62f6c17a04513f.webm?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/777213f909e4b8e94e62f6c17a04513f.mp4?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/31a3348f08c406a9de891a1ec4f37ba9.webp?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=47 /></span><br><br>Every soldier matters. Good teamwork and communication is essential to win. Using unique roles, soldiers can work together to manage resources, deploy necessary vehicles, build strategic forward operating bases, and lead others into battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/5b75af5239e442ea6dc14b70e8aae2ff.poster.avif?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/5b75af5239e442ea6dc14b70e8aae2ff.webm?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/5b75af5239e442ea6dc14b70e8aae2ff.mp4?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/442449d0f5d5806477b8335f196f3aef.webp?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=47 /></span><br><br>Advance to the frontlines in 27 vs 27 head-to-head combat. Decide your loadout from any of the 7 distinct infantry roles and take advantage of crucial equipment and different weapons. Fight as a Squad Leader, Rifleman, Medic, Support, Marksman, Demolition, or Engineer alongside your squad members. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/35a038c7064bf24876372f422f6f8c5c.poster.avif?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/35a038c7064bf24876372f422f6f8c5c.webm?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/35a038c7064bf24876372f422f6f8c5c.mp4?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/f4f85ca6603b0d4e587ed6813c205f7c.webp?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=47 /></span><br><br>Resource management is key to continue fighting your opponent. A logistics vehicle can hold both construction points and ammo. Construction points allow squad leaders to place down offensive and defensive buildings, and ammo can be gathered by soldiers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/e9cc13ef9c041b1c1dd13a42934bfddf.poster.avif?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/e9cc13ef9c041b1c1dd13a42934bfddf.webm?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/e9cc13ef9c041b1c1dd13a42934bfddf.mp4?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/47a3e410ed32499013b0394209edbe2a.webp?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=47 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Release Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> At least 3 maps<br></li><li> Buildable objects that will give you an advantage on the battlefield<br></li><li> Light vehicles (MRAP and Logi Truck)<br></li><li> Team specific weapons<br></li><li> Class specific weapons including the mine, satchel charge, RPG, repair wrench, medic bag, etc.<br></li><li> Stats and Leaderboards <br></li><li> Ranks</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Operation Valor is a tactical top-down multiplayer shooter that provides large-scale combat through base building and teamwork. Players will fight across diverse battlefields with squad-based action in vehicles, or on foot. Prepare for an exciting battle utilizing strategy, logistics, and base building. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/777213f909e4b8e94e62f6c17a04513f.poster.avif?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/777213f909e4b8e94e62f6c17a04513f.webm?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/777213f909e4b8e94e62f6c17a04513f.mp4?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/31a3348f08c406a9de891a1ec4f37ba9.webp?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=47 /></span><br><br>Every soldier matters. Good teamwork and communication is essential to win. Using unique roles, soldiers can work together to manage resources, deploy necessary vehicles, build strategic forward operating bases, and lead others into battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/5b75af5239e442ea6dc14b70e8aae2ff.poster.avif?t=1751559815\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/5b75af5239e442ea6dc14b70e8aae2ff.webm?t=1751559815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/5b75af5239e442ea6dc14b70e8aae2f